reviewText: I am glad to know these safety facts about my Dryer, Water Heater and Chimney vents. Scary.... Time to pull out my calendar and set up an inspection and cleaning. Now I know what that white powder is on my bricks.
I'm not a firefighter, but I bought this DVD because I wanted to learn how to make my home a safer place to be. I really learned some things that I had never heard anywhere before!
